title: [Vornavian Coast, Beached Hulk]
description: This compartment is almost completely underwater.  Small waves mimic the tide outside and wash repeatedly along the bulkhead.  Small fish can be seen darting in the water, indicating a hole in the hull below the surface of the water.  A louvered door leads to the hold to the northwest.
